$ Power Query M formula language: #shared

`#shared` is an intrinsic variable whose value is a record that contains the names and values of all shared section members currently in scope.

In a «top-level context», the simple expression `#shared` shows all *global objects*:
gh|about-Power-Query-Formula-M|/language/keywords/_shared/img/_shared.png||

`#shared` is especially useful in the → Microsoft/Power-Query/M-formula/standard-library function → Microsoft/Power-Query/M-formula/standard-library/Expression/Evaluate[`Expression.Evaluate`] to pass as the
→ Microsoft/Power-Query/M-formula/standard-library/Expression/Evaluate#Expression-Evaluate-shared[environment parameter].
